  <brief_title>Iron Absorption and Utilization in Adolescents Infected With Malaria Parasites, Hookworms or Schistosoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Iron Absorption and Utilization in Adolescents Infected With Malaria Parasites, Hookworms or Schistosoma.</official_title>
